	 		FAUST : a programming language for
	 		  audio applications and plugins
					==============
	 Grame, Centre National de Creation Musicale
	 			 http://www.grame.fr



BUILDING LIBFAUST ON VISUAL STUDIO
----------------------------------

1- Compile dependencies
	LLVM
	openssl
	
2- Copy template.props and name it faust.props
	
3- Modify faust.props with the paths to your dependencies



tested on visual studio 2012 with LLVM 3.4
